  "translations": {
    "en": "He, peace be upon him, wrote back: \"I have understood your letter and what you have mentioned about your father. God willing, I shall never cease supplicating for you. Compliance is better for you than open confrontation. And with hardship comes ease. So be patient, for the end result is for the God-conscious. May Allah keep you firm on the authority of those whom you have accepted. You and we are all entrusted in the care of Allah, and with Him no trust is ever lost.\"",
